{"tid":1260893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"下次塗鴉破壞前可唔可以諗諗先","createTime":"2019-06-27T03:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T04:07:07.000Z","uid":97941,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1299ade13dbd3d25a5f2bc68b187fdef08fe03a2","tid":1260893,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T03:53:15.000Z","msg":"我明白，兄弟爬山各有各做<br />\n唔係話政治潔癖，警察就打人<br />\n我地就連畫下畫表達不滿都唔俾<br />\n只係希望大家針對番訴求去表達意見<br />\n例如畫屎畫鳩拆字，同我地嘅訴求冇乜關係<br />\n就會變左我地只係一班純發洩嘅示威者，對件事冇大幫助<br />\n<br />\n雖然一諗到班狗見到自己嗰狗竇搞成咁、好嬲豬嗰樣就覺得好爽<br />\n但我地依家打緊輿論戰<br />\n會俾位人入、非必要嘅行動就麻煩各位大佬盡量避免<br />\n<br />\n琴晚嘅事唔發生都發生左<br />\n都希望大家唔好再怪責，反省完就再上路<br />\n未出嚟嘅快啲出門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c7ce5c6206dc344d17aa0723243117842cb73d","tid":1260893,"uid":20431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T04:00:37.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"6d15496b56282047b069b69344ae6dd87268a2e1","tid":1260893,"uid":64131,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T04:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ih1.redbubble.net/image.11592754.2428/fc,550x550,white.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fih1.redbubble.net%2Fimage.11592754.2428%2Ffc%2C550x550%2Cwhite.jpg&h=27ce45e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"edc2650ed3ad26c2713ac4ce7527e4f35140a6d6","tid":1260893,"uid":97941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T04:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc2da8c60b4d18183462c7ee84c2c4ccdfac100","tid":1260893,"uid":81692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T04:07:07.000Z","msg":"簡單d講係麻煩下次噴靚少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}